    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Lightning springs from your hand to deliver a shock to a creature you touch. Make a melee spell attack against the target. You have advantage on the attack roll if the target is wearing metal armor or armor that lacks the Natural Materials property. On a hit, the target takes [[/damage]] damage, and it can’t take reactions until the start of its next turn.</p><p>The spell’s damage increases by 1d8 when you reach 5th level ([[/damage 2d8 lightning]]{2d8}), 11th level ([[/damage 3d8 lightning]]{3d8}), and 17th level ([[/damage 4d8 lightning]]{4d8}).</p>",
